    <h2 id="roles_responsibilities">Roles &amp; Responsibilities</h2>
    <ul>
        <li><span style="color:#087b08"><strong>Commander</strong></span> - Leader of the Unit.
            <ul>
                <li>Execute the orders of their superior.</li>
                <li>Instruct the driver on where and how to move the vehicle.</li>
                <li>Setting scan sectors for the gunner.</li>
                <li>Instructing the gunner to engage a target (CIE).</li>
                <li>Communicate and coordinate with other elements on the battlefield.</li>
                <li>Operate the vehicle's countermeasures.</li>
            </ul></li>
    </ul>
    <ul>
        <li><span style="color:#087b08"><strong>Driver</strong></span> - Operates the vehicle's movement.
            <ul>
                <li>Control the vehicle.</li>
                <li>Spot threats to the vehicle during movement, like mines and IEDs.</li>
                <li>Operate the Engine Smoke generator System (ESS).</li>
